                  </persName>
            . I am a news-vender. I was at the public-house, and saw the prisoner take the watch from the prosecutor's fob, he sat in the same box with him; he went out, and returned in about ten minutes. I accused him of it, he denied it. The watch was never found. I gave him in charge.</p>
